overview: Mrs. Marni, a successful pottery entrepreneur, is busy getting her shop ready to open  after being closed for a long time due to the pandemic. At that moment, his employees, Tresno and Bejo, found a towering pile of cardboard inside the shop. Tresno and Bejo, who were suspicious about the contents of the box, finally tried to find out what Mrs. Marni was planning. Unexpectedly, the search ended in facts that they had never thought possible.
title: Ubag-Ubeg
